caption: Had a great experience at Ensemble HTX.  They’re a new venture and just established a new dining venue.  Good was great, ambiance was a lot of fun, loved the team and the BYOB.  Would highly recommend for a quality, unique experience!

We had such a great time. It was really wonderful to go in with a surprise waiting for us. The food was phenomenal and you can easily tell this is a passion project for them. Every item was thoughtfully curated and tasty. We will definitely be back!
Amazing 6 course dinner. Each magnificently prepared and presented.

What an amazing experience! If you want to get away from this busy world and be able to get back to enjoying conversation with people while enjoying some impeccable food & service this is the new spot in HTX to check out! The mole was so ridiculously good that I forgot to take a picture of it! 🤦‍♂️
